<elements>
  <!-- ========================= -->
  <!-- Race: Elysian Dragon-Kin   -->
  <!-- ========================= -->
  <element name="Elysian Dragon-Kin" type="Race" source="Traveler's Guide to Elysia" id="ID_ELYSIA_RACE_DRAGON_KIN">
    <description>
      <h4>Dragon-Kin</h4>
      <p>Dragon-Kin are humanoids who carry draconic blood not as a distant echo, but as a living inheritance. Unlike dragonborn, whose lineage manifests uniformly, Dragon-Kin display their heritage in varied and personal ways—through antler-like horns, patches of shimmering scales, and tails that move with deliberate balance.</p>
      <p>Their draconic ancestry is ancient rather than immediate. At some point deep within their lineage, a dragon became bound to a mortal bloodline through means long lost to history. Once established, this inheritance does not fade or dilute over generations. A Dragon-Kin family remains draconic indefinitely, which is both the source of their power and the reason for their rarity.</p>
      <p>Though uncommon, Dragon-Kin often integrate seamlessly into the cultures they inhabit, identifying more with the societies that raised them than with any unified Dragon-Kin culture.</p>

      <h4>Dragon-Kin Traits</h4>
      <p>Your Dragon-Kin character has the following racial traits.</p>

      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Ability Score Increase.</em></strong> Increase two different ability scores of your choice by 1.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Size.</em></strong> Your size is Medium.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Speed.</em></strong> Your walking speed is 30 feet.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Languages.</em></strong> You can speak, read, and write Common and Draconic.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Darkvision.</em></strong> You have darkvision out to 30 feet. In addition, you have advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on sight.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Draconic Will.</em></strong> You have advantage on saving throws against being charmed or frightened.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Cultural Adaptation.</em></strong> You gain proficiency with one tool of your choice, or you learn one additional language of your choice.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Draconic Insight.</em></strong> You gain proficiency in two of the following skills of your choice: Perception, Nature, Survival, or Insight.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Draconic Expression.</em></strong> Choose one: Great Wings, Draconic Magic, or Great Horns.</p>
      <p class="indent"><strong><em>Draconic Color.</em></strong> Choose one draconic color. Your color determines your draconic damage type and grants resistance to that damage type.</p>
    </description>

    <sheet display="false" />

    <setters>
      <!-- Optional polish: names/height/weight like official races -->
      <set name="names" type="male">Auren, Caelis, Drazan, Eryndor, Kaelith, Mavren, Orryx, Rhavon, Soryn, Veydran</set>
      <set name="names" type="female">Astra, Calyra, Draeva, Eiryn, Kaelara, Myrris, Nyvara, Rhaela, Saphira, Velyss</set>
      <set name="names" type="clan">Ashscale, Brightwing, Cindertalon, Dawncrest, Emberborn, Frostvein, Ironsong, Stormbrand, Voidcoil, Wyrmspire</set>
      <set name="names-format">{{name}} of {{clan}}</set>

      <!-- Lightweight defaults; tweak later if you want more exact physiology -->
      <set name="height" modifier="2d10">4'10"</set>
      <set name="weight" modifier="2d6">120 lb.</set>
    </setters>

    <rules>
      <stat name="innate speed" value="30" bonus="base" />
      <grant type="Language" id="ID_LANGUAGE_COMMON" />
      <grant type="Language" id="ID_LANGUAGE_DRACONIC" />

      <grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_ELYSIA_TRAIT_DRAGON_KIN_ASI" />
      <grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_ELYSIA_TRAIT_DRAGON_KIN_DARKVISION_30" />
      <grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_ELYSIA_TRAIT_DRAGON_KIN_DRACONIC_WILL" />
      <grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_ELYSIA_TRAIT_DRAGON_KIN_CULTURAL_ADAPTATION" />
      <grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_ELYSIA_TRAIT_DRAGON_KIN_DRACONIC_INSIGHT" />
      <grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_ELYSIA_TRAIT_DRAGON_KIN_EXPRESSION" />

      <grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_ELYSIA_TRAIT_DRAGON_KIN_COLOR" />
      <grant type="Racial Trait" id="ID_ELYSIA_TRAIT_DRAGON_KIN_DAMAGE_RESISTANCE" />
    </rules>
  </element>

